            <h2>ðŸš¨ GAME OVER ðŸš¨</h2>
            <p>A balloon escaped! The beat stopped!</p>
            <p class="final-score-text">FINAL SCORE: <span id="final-score">0</span></p>
            <label for="player-name">ENTER NAME:</label>
